OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday cloudy to start with some
OL,7,Flight rain. Drier and brighter later.
OL,8,FWednesday and Thursday, dry with long
OL,9,Fsunny spells. Temperatures generally
OL,10,Fnear average inland.
